1
00:00:03,803 --> 00:00:04,938
Hey guys!

2
00:00:07,841 --> 00:00:08,775
Come a little closer.

3
00:00:08,775 --> 00:00:09,442
I can't see you.

4
00:00:09,442 --> 00:00:10,210
Hold on a second.

5
00:00:15,248 --> 00:00:16,916
Are we doing anything special today?

6
00:00:16,916 --> 00:00:17,951
What we're doing today is...

7
00:00:17,951 --> 00:00:19,652
a training camp for a brand collab.

8
00:00:19,652 --> 00:00:20,887
Our mission for today is...

9
00:00:21,521 --> 00:00:23,423
Hei Yan is going to sing for everyone.

10
00:01:09,135 --> 00:01:10,103
Alright, alright.

11
00:01:10,637 --> 00:01:11,538
The thing is...

12
00:01:11,738 --> 00:01:12,605
he has a bit of a cold.

13
00:01:12,605 --> 00:01:13,973
He even had a fever yesterday.

14
00:01:13,973 --> 00:01:15,008
So...

15
00:01:15,809 --> 00:01:16,810
please bear with him.

16
00:01:17,677 --> 00:01:18,745
Say something!

17
00:01:18,745 --> 00:01:19,779
Don't make me do all the talking.

18
00:01:22,549 --> 00:01:23,683
Since Bai Xing took care of me,

19
00:01:23,683 --> 00:01:25,919
I'm feeling a lot better.

20
00:01:27,954 --> 00:01:29,389
Let me see...

21
00:01:29,389 --> 00:01:30,957
what the comments are saying.

22
00:01:32,525 --> 00:01:33,159
Hei Yan.

23
00:01:33,593 --> 00:01:34,928
I'll ask, you answer.

24
00:01:34,928 --> 00:01:36,529
Otherwise, you're just like a prop.

25
00:01:37,230 --> 00:01:37,797
Fine.

26
00:01:38,164 --> 00:01:38,998
First question.

27
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:42,001
Do we...

28
00:01:43,470 --> 00:01:44,704
sleep together?

29
00:01:48,875 --> 00:01:50,276
What do we wear to bed?

30
00:01:51,111 --> 00:01:51,945
Clothes.

31
00:01:53,179 --> 00:01:54,881
What color underwear do you like?

32
00:01:55,648 --> 00:01:56,416
That's our business.

33
00:01:56,416 --> 00:01:57,484
We don't need to tell them that.

34
00:02:00,954 --> 00:02:03,523
What exactly is this
brand collaboration about?

35
00:02:04,557 --> 00:02:05,658
Photoshoots.

36
00:02:05,658 --> 00:02:06,793
A short film.

37
00:02:06,793 --> 00:02:07,894
Music.

38
00:02:08,495 --> 00:02:09,329
And performances.

39
00:02:09,329 --> 00:02:10,230
Something like that.

40
00:02:10,611 --> 00:02:13,644
[The comments are unanimously positive]

41
00:02:14,934 --> 00:02:16,236
Are you two playing...

42
00:02:16,236 --> 00:02:18,571
a couple or is it just a bromance?

43
00:02:21,307 --> 00:02:22,375
Stay tuned!

44
00:02:22,375 --> 00:02:23,243
That's about all the time we have.

45
00:02:23,243 --> 00:02:23,843
Bye!

46
00:02:25,445 --> 00:02:26,646
Stay tuned to B&amp;W.

47
00:02:26,646 --> 00:02:27,447
If there's any news,

48
00:02:27,447 --> 00:02:28,581
we'll be sure to let you know.

49
00:02:28,948 --> 00:02:29,883
Bye-bye!

50
00:02:32,452 --> 00:02:33,453
You're not saving the stream?

51
00:02:33,453 --> 00:02:34,087
No.

52
00:02:34,988 --> 00:02:35,722
Why not?

53
00:02:35,722 --> 00:02:37,090
It was great.

54
00:02:37,090 --> 00:02:38,791
It'd be a shame not to save it.

55
00:02:38,791 --> 00:02:39,726
The things you can't have...

56
00:02:39,726 --> 00:02:40,827
are always the most precious.
